reviewText: Lots of Action here. Rita Cansino (Rita Hayworth ) mentioned and seen here as a very beautiful young  government agent. One of the highlights is when TEX sings at the Rodeo an unforgettable song about a cowboy dying. Note  Rita's stunning young looks when she watches Tex singing. Tex, undercover,  nabs the culprits who make the horses loose at the rodeo and then try to  steal the rodeo money .
